      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=tgb1ber6in]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=tgb1ber6in]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=qvgnxi5l5n]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qvgnxi5l5n]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ard72xbkt0]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ard72xbkt0]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=opwww52k5l]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=opwww52k5l]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=hml3qd3db9]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hml3qd3db9]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=hmqcys2s3r]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=hmqcys2s3r]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ijklkn74u0]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ijklkn74u0]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=e2f5t14xbk]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=e2f5t14xbk]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=dn0us3s13g]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=dn0us3s13g]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=cs6gbm8icw]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cs6gbm8icw]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" width=\"102\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689949980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689949980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"73\" data-width=\"59\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"562626620\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"3e8cc5e1-9ee4-4879-a521-cc2bf771f8ee\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689949980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689949980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73 1x\" /></span><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"FirstContact_Final.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/FirstContact_Final.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689976088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/FirstContact_Final.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689976088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"562692144\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"FirstContact_Final.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"d4839ea5-b623-4cbb-974c-7049c60316a5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/FirstContact_Final.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689976088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/FirstContact_Final.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755689976088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ijklkn74u0\">Project</span></strong>:  The Hunted</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"opwww52k5l\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Eugene Riecansky</p><p>I made this image as the launch teaser for the latest RenderMan Art Challenge and gave myself three weeks from start to finish.  </p><p>Enjoy the breakdown from how I came up with the initial story and concept, through to texturing, lighting, and compositing the final render.</p><hr /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/563478530\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_lookdev3.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lookdev3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755697663082&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lookdev3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755697663082&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"563314702\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_lookdev3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"8d138f1f-2960-4b17-bcfa-4cc15309338e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lookdev3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755697663082&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lookdev3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755697663082&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-Story,Story&amp;Story\"><span data-colorid=\"dn0us3s13g\">Story, Story &amp; Story</span></h1><p>Starting with a strong story beat is crucial.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/568557635/The+Hunted+Refs\" data-linked-resource-id=\"568557635\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"huntedrefs.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/huntedrefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681161100&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/huntedrefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681161100&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657392211\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"huntedrefs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"f66f6d83-fccc-4c55-be32-ed882cdc9cc0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/huntedrefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681161100&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/huntedrefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762681161100&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-GatheringReferences\"><span data-colorid=\"hml3qd3db9\">Gathering References</span></h1><p>Starting with a strong story beat is crucial.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/563118083\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_textures3.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868428612&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868428612&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567246927\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_textures3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"3bf1609f-4d26-476a-b32d-3b61b16b0100\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868428612&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868428612&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-MakingTheVan\"><span data-colorid=\"e2f5t14xbk\">Making The Van</span></h1><p>Creating the UFO-hunting van character</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/567509003\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_textures2.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures2.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755868448546&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures2.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755868448546&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"563314708\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_textures2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"34a442fe-a755-4f83-991d-b2690e407dea\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures2.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755868448546&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_textures2.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755868448546&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-Texturing\"><span data-colorid=\"ard72xbkt0\">Texturing</span></h1><p>Using textures to enhance the character and story</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/567279687\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_usd2.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_usd2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868603050&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_usd2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868603050&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567476225\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_usd2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"8cfb2b68-5d4e-4a81-980c-2c83782cb65d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_usd2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868603050&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_usd2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868603050&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-USDAssets\"><span data-colorid=\"hmqcys2s3r\">USD Assets</span></h1><p>Why a USD workflow allows for a super creative workflow, no matter if you&rsquo;re a single artist or a large studio</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/567509019\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_layout.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_layout.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868650653&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_layout.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868650653&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567246934\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_layout.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"eed97728-4c71-448a-9249-9836b229bebc\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_layout.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868650653&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_layout.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868650653&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-Layout\"><span data-colorid=\"tgb1ber6in\">Layout</span></h1><p>USD + XPU is perfect for layout and scene creation.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/567083091\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_lighting3.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lighting3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868692258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lighting3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868692258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567279681\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_lighting3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"014e320f-6a2c-4222-825d-0d964fa33643\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lighting3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868692258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_lighting3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1755868692258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-Lighting\"><span data-colorid=\"qvgnxi5l5n\">Lighting</span></h1><p>Sky, UFO, and van lighting are all key</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/567017582/The+Hunted+Finalizing\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567017582\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_rendering3.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_rendering3.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755869204199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562823215/RenderManUniversity_rendering3.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755869204199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"567246940\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_rendering3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"34\" data-media-id=\"23b3a4ec-35c7-43d8-83f0-318a7d952551\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_rendering3.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755869204199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562823215/RenderManUniversity_rendering3.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1755869204199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"TheHunted-Finalizing\"><span data-colorid=\"cs6gbm8icw\">Finalizing</span></h1><p>Time to render out the final image and refine it in comp</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><p /><p /><p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
